Introduction

  • In this LAB we have conducted data visualization on the data which consists of different Signal Strength and ASU's reading taken at various places within BIAS campus and througout the Bhimtal Lake
  • First we import the 2 CSV's files containing data within BIAS campus and within the Bhimtal Lake.
  • Then we installed the following libraries :
    1. matplotlib and seaborn to visualize our data
    2. pandas to clean and process data
  • After that we do some data cleaning using pandas , for eg:
    1. Renaming the coloumn name so that we can process them.
    2. Removing the decimal values so that we can plot graph out of them .
    3. Removing NaN and Null values to remove discrepancy.
  • After that We have performed the data visualization.

Conclusion

      


        BIAS Campus and the area surrounding bhimtal lake has enough 4G Signal band reach, the signals were never too
        low, and the spots with government office and tourist point of interests had the maximum strength recorded.
        Inside the campus, the New building has the best signal average. The signal distribution was very uniform except
        a few points of lacking. Overall the result was a satisfactory distributed of Bandwidth, for both low end and
        mid range smartphone processor modem to recieve for Airtel Sim Users.
